@page
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "How It Works";
}

<div class="container py-5">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-10 mx-auto">
            <h1 class="display-4 text-center mb-4">How CampusConnect Works for Students</h1>
            <p class="lead text-center mb-5">
                Unlock your career potential with CampusConnect. We make it easy to discover opportunities, connect with employers, and launch your professional journey.
            </p>

            <div class="row text-center mb-5">
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                    <div class="p-4 border rounded shadow-sm h-100">
                        <i class="fas fa-user-circle fa-3x text-primary mb-3"></i>
                        <h3 class="h5 mb-3">1. Create Your Profile</h3>
                        <p>Showcase your skills, experience, and aspirations. Build a comprehensive profile that highlights your academic achievements, projects, work history, and extracurricular activities. A strong profile is your first step to catching an employer's eye!</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                    <div class="p-4 border rounded shadow-sm h-100">
                        <i class="fas fa-search fa-3x text-primary mb-3"></i>
                        <h3 class="h5 mb-3">2. Discover Opportunities</h3>
                        <p>Explore thousands of job and internship listings from a wide range of companies – from innovative startups to Fortune 500 corporations. Use our powerful search filters to find roles that match your interests, major, and location preferences.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                    <div class="p-4 border rounded shadow-sm h-100">
                        <i class="fas fa-paper-plane fa-3x text-primary mb-3"></i>
                        <h3 class="h5 mb-3">3. Apply with Ease</h3>
                        <p>Once you find an opportunity that excites you, applying is straightforward. Submit your profile and resume directly through CampusConnect. Keep track of your applications and get notified about their status.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row text-center mb-5">
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                    <div class="p-4 border rounded shadow-sm h-100">
                        <i class="fas fa-comments fa-3x text-primary mb-3"></i>
                        <h3 class="h5 mb-3">4. Connect with Employers</h3>
                        <p>Engage with recruiters and industry professionals. Attend virtual career fairs, info sessions, and networking events hosted on CampusConnect. Ask questions, learn about company cultures, and make valuable connections.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                    <div class="p-4 border rounded shadow-sm h-100">
                        <i class="fas fa-calendar-alt fa-3x text-primary mb-3"></i>
                        <h3 class="h5 mb-3">5. Attend Events & Workshops</h3>
                        <p>Your university's career center and employers post workshops, career fairs, and other events. Participate to gain new skills, learn about different industries, and expand your professional network.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                    <div class="p-4 border rounded shadow-sm h-100">
                        <i class="fas fa-lightbulb fa-3x text-primary mb-3"></i>
                        <h3 class="h5 mb-3">6. Access Career Resources</h3>
                        <p>Benefit from a wealth of resources, including resume building tips, interview preparation guides, and career advice articles. CampusConnect is more than just a job board – it's your partner in career development.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center">
                <h2 class="h3 mb-3">Ready to Get Started?</h2>
                <p class="mb-4">Your future starts now. Sign up or log in to CampusConnect and take the next step in your career journey!</p>
                @* Add a link to the registration or login page if available *@
                @* <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Sign Up Today</a> *@
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>